<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA82">
<l>cārntārkkup poṟkoḻuntē yottilaṅkic cārātu</l>
<l>pērntārkkut tīkkoṭiyiṉ peṟṟiyatān - tērntuṇari</l>
<l>ṟāḻcuṭarōṉ ceṅkatiruñ cāyun taḻalvaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>vīḻcaṭaiyē yeṉṟuraikku miṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Shining like a golden tendril to those who approach, to those who return</l>
<l>without approaching it has the properties of a fire banner – the lightning</l>
<l>that talks of the descending matted hair of the fire-coloured one</l>
<l>by whom the red beams of the sinking sun are bowed (~ humiliated).</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
